text: Takaya Kawanabe (born 22 December 1988) is a retired Japanese football player. Kawanabe signed for Omiya Ardija in 2007. In 2011, he moved to Tanjong Pagar United FC and scored 9 goals in 36 appearances for the club. In February 2013 Kawanabe joined the Latvian Higher League club FC JÅ«rmala. Later he played with FK Mladost Podgorica in the Montenegrin First League and next with FK Rudar Prijedor in the Premier League of Bosnia and Herzegovina.
